title: Modern Downtown Loft with Skyline Views
description: Stunning modern loft featuring floor-to-ceiling windows with breathtaking skyline views. This sophisticated residence offers an open-concept living space with high-end finishes throughout. The chef's kitchen boasts custom cabinetry, quartz countertops, and premium stainless steel appliances. Master suite includes a spa-like bathroom with soaking tub and walk-in shower. Building amenities include 24-hour concierge, fitness center, and rooftop terrace.

title: Charming Victorian Home with Garden
description: Beautifully restored Victorian home in the heart of the city. This architectural gem features original details including crown molding, bay windows, and hardwood floors, seamlessly blended with modern amenities. Spacious rooms with high ceilings create an elegant living experience. The gourmet kitchen opens to a private garden oasis perfect for entertaining. Updated systems throughout ensure modern comfort in this historic treasure.

title: Luxury Beachfront Penthouse
description: Unparalleled luxury living in this oceanfront penthouse with panoramic Atlantic views. This meticulously designed residence features an expansive great room with 12-foot ceilings and floor-to-ceiling impact glass. The gourmet kitchen showcases top-of-the-line Wolf and Sub-Zero appliances. Private elevator access leads to your personal oasis. Two wraparound terraces provide over 1,000 sq ft of outdoor living space. White-glove service and world-class amenities complete this extraordinary offering.

title: Cozy Craftsman Bungalow
description: Quintessential Portland craftsman bungalow in a walkable neighborhood. Original character details include built-in cabinetry, wainscoting, and a charming front porch. The home has been thoughtfully updated with a renovated kitchen featuring butcher block counters and vintage-style fixtures. Hardwood floors throughout, period lighting, and a beautiful brick fireplace. The backyard is a private retreat with mature trees and raised garden beds. Close to restaurants, shops, and parks.

title: Contemporary Townhouse in Historic District
description: Exquisite contemporary townhouse in Boston's most desirable neighborhood. This sun-filled residence features an open floor plan with designer finishes throughout. The main level includes a sophisticated living and dining area with gas fireplace. The chef's kitchen boasts custom cabinetry, Carrara marble, and high-end appliances. Upper floors house three generous bedrooms including a master suite with spa bath. Private roof deck with city views. Steps to restaurants, shopping, and public transportation.

title: Mountain View Ranch Estate
description: Spectacular ranch-style estate on 3 acres with breathtaking mountain views. This custom-built home features vaulted ceilings, massive windows, and an open great room perfect for entertaining. The gourmet kitchen includes professional-grade appliances and a large island. Master wing offers privacy with sitting area, spa-like bath, and dual walk-in closets. Additional features include a finished walkout basement, home office, and three-car garage. Outdoor spaces include multiple patios, fire pit, and room for horses.

title: Sleek Urban Studio Apartment
description: Sophisticated studio in the heart of Capitol Hill. This efficiently designed space maximizes every square foot with clever built-ins and Murphy bed. Floor-to-ceiling windows flood the space with natural light. Modern kitchen features stainless appliances and quartz counters. Building amenities include rooftop deck with stunning views, fitness center, and secure bike storage. Walk to shops, restaurants, and light rail. Perfect for urban professionals or investment property.

title: Historic Brownstone with Modern Renovation
description: Impeccably renovated brownstone blending historic charm with contemporary luxury. Original details including exposed brick, tin ceilings, and marble mantels complement the sleek modern updates. Chef's kitchen with waterfall island opens to a landscaped garden. Multiple living spaces across four floors provide flexibility. Master floor features two bedrooms and spa bathroom. Finished basement includes media room and home gym. Prime location near Brooklyn Heights Promenade and all transit.

title: Desert Oasis with Pool and Guest House
description: Stunning desert contemporary home with breathtaking mountain views. This architectural masterpiece features walls of glass, soaring ceilings, and seamless indoor-outdoor living. The great room flows to covered patios and resort-style backyard with infinity pool, spa, and outdoor kitchen. Gourmet kitchen includes high-end appliances and custom cabinetry. Master retreat offers spa bathroom and private patio. Detached guest house perfect for visitors or rental income. Solar panels included.

title: Lakefront Cottage with Private Dock
description: Rare lakefront opportunity with private dock and sandy beach. This charming cottage offers the ultimate Lake Tahoe lifestyle with panoramic water views from every room. Vaulted ceilings with exposed beams, stone fireplace, and walls of windows create a warm mountain retreat. Updated kitchen opens to deck with outdoor dining area. Master suite with balcony overlooks the lake. Lower level includes guest bedrooms and family room. Launch your kayak from your own private beach. Year-round access.

title: Minimalist Loft in Arts District
description: Sophisticated industrial loft in the vibrant Arts District. This light-filled space features 14-foot ceilings, polished concrete floors, and exposed ductwork. Open floor plan includes a sleek kitchen with European appliances and Caesar stone counters. Floor-to-ceiling windows overlook bustling streets. Master bedroom suite with custom closets. Building offers rooftop deck with skyline views, gym, and secured parking. Walk to galleries, restaurants, and entertainment.

title: Colonial Revival with Modern Amenities
description: Gracious Colonial Revival on a tree-lined street near Lake Michigan. This classic home has been extensively updated while preserving original charm. Formal living and dining rooms feature crown molding and hardwood floors. The kitchen renovation includes white cabinetry, marble counters, and top appliances. Family room addition with vaulted ceiling and fireplace. Upstairs includes five bedrooms and renovated baths. Finished basement with rec room. Beautifully landscaped yard with patio. Walk to beach, shops, and Metra.
